## Decision Precedence

1. **Safety** — never set timer params to 0, never zero out safety rails
2. **Lessons** — high-confidence validated lessons override forecast-based reasoning
{% if replan_mode %}3. **Replan** — observed conditions override forecast-derived tactics for next 24h
